{"tid":1929442,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：今日將向全球發紅色外遊警示　中澳台除外　抵港者需強制檢疫14日","createTime":"2020-03-17T02:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T03:14:21.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7355fdc4b14251d3f27b28b99eb648fdbbbb9d93","tid":1929442,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:52:41.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥今早（17日）在行政會議前會見記者，表示各國確診個案近日呈爆發性上升，加上過去兩周的確診個案有九成屬輸入個案，疫情再次進入嚴峻階段，她表示今日內會向全球其他國家地區發出紅色外遊警示，內地、澳門及台灣除外。<br />\n<br />\n她亦宣布，本周四（19日）凌晨零時起所有抵港的人需接受14日強制檢疫及醫學監察。"},{"pid":"91fed596799420c0f15b4e61752f0b64405cdf6b","tid":1929442,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:52:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200317/s00001/1584410909733/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200317%2Fs00001%2F1584410909733%2F&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8BZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=1ecd3805\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200317%2Fs00001%2F1584410909733%2F&h=da1ebbb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200317/s00001/1584410909733/</a>"},{"pid":"1e3d417c40fac60ac55def65bbea89e5b11488ae","tid":1929442,"uid":31370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"繼續復工啦"},{"pid":"c6962cf6ce0d3db5309eaee89e76b2df030dcbcb","tid":1929442,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:57:27.000Z","msg":"支那除外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b422fe95ac03de1bc4014fde6fa4d70140086ace","tid":1929442,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:58:32.000Z","msg":"即支那來港解除14日？<img src=\"/ass